    <item>
      <title>他们与法律抗争，法律获胜：解读</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-08/uk-politics-latest-keir-starmer-leans-on-rule-of-law-to-quell-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国法院正遭遇史上最大规模的积压案件，数以万计的案件等待审理。与此同时，监狱已接近饱和，98.4% 的囚犯已被占用，监狱部长们被迫提前释放囚犯以腾出空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-08/uk-politics-latest-keir-starmer-leans-on-rule-of-law-to-quell-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 16:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲疾病预防控制中心计划宣布区域性 Mpo 疫情为紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/africa-cdc-plans-to-declare-regional-mpox-outbreak-an-emergency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲地区首席卫生咨询机构将首次动用这一权力，非洲迅速蔓延的猪瘟疫情很可能在下周被宣布为非洲大陆安全的突发公共卫生事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/africa-cdc-plans-to-declare-regional-mpox-outbreak-an-emergency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:59:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国网络间谍计划建立人工智能“实验室”以应对敌对国家的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/uk-cyber-spies-plan-ai-lab-to-counter-hostile-state-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国间谍机构正在加大力度应对来自敌对外国的网络和人工智能威胁，包括过去 10 天引发全国骚乱的那种网络操纵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/uk-cyber-spies-plan-ai-lab-to-counter-hostile-state-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:55:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>商业团体称特鲁多的临时居民上限可能对经济造成损害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trudeau-s-temporary-resident-cap-risks-economic-harm-business-groups-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大独立商业倡导者表示，总理贾斯汀·特鲁多减少临时移民的计划可能会带来严重的经济后果，凸显出政府在试图减缓人口增长时面临的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trudeau-s-temporary-resident-cap-risks-economic-harm-business-groups-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登计划加快项目历史保护审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/biden-aims-to-speed-up-historic-preservation-reviews-in-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的政府正在采取措施，加快涉及历史建筑的项目许可和审查，这是在美国社区建设基础设施和气候适应力的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/biden-aims-to-speed-up-historic-preservation-reviews-in-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯因乌克兰军队袭击宣布边境地区进入紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/russia-calls-kursk-emergency-after-kyiv-sends-troops-over-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军队对俄罗斯领土发动了自两年多前克里姆林宫发动战争以来最大规模的入侵，俄罗斯陆军首席瓦列里·格拉西莫夫因此面临越来越多的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/russia-calls-kursk-emergency-after-kyiv-sends-troops-over-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:10:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尤努斯宣誓担任孟加拉国政府首席顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/nobel-winner-yunus-arrives-in-bangladesh-to-lead-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺贝尔经济学奖得主穆罕默德·尤努斯宣誓就任孟加拉国临时政府首席顾问。几天前，学生主导的抗议活动迫使总理谢赫·哈西娜下台并逃离该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/nobel-winner-yunus-arrives-in-bangladesh-to-lead-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙警方追捕回国的加泰罗尼亚分离主义分子普伊格蒙特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/catalan-separatist-puigdemont-defies-courts-with-return-to-spain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙警方正在追捕卡莱斯·普伊格蒙特 (Carles Puigdemont)。此前，这位前加泰罗尼亚主席在巴塞罗那市中心的一场集会上短暂露面。尽管收到了逮捕令，他还是结束了近七年的自我流放，回到了西班牙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/catalan-separatist-puigdemont-defies-courts-with-return-to-spain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 07:26:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
